        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arco</ex></expan> Cornelio Oc<lb break="no" n="2"/>taviano <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>iro</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>erfectissimo</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>praef</abbr><ex>ecto</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/>classis <expan><abbr>praet</abbr><ex>oriae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Misen</abbr><ex>ensis</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/>duci per Africam <lb n="5"/>Numidiam Maureta<lb break="no" n="6"/>niamque splendi<lb break="no" n="7"/>dissimus ordo <lb n="8"/>municipi Bisicensis <lb n="9"/>patrono incompara<lb break="no" n="10"/>bili ob merita
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Datierung: nicht vor etwa 260 n. Chr., als der Geehrte Flottenpräfekt gewesen sein dürfte.</p>
            </div>
